#: addons/sumatran_world.wad/addon:2
msgid "Sumatran World"
msgstr "El món de Sumatra"

#: addons/sumatran_world.wad/addon:3
msgid ""
"Modifies world for Sumatran tribe. The changes affect Amazons too. Tropical "
"trees do not grow on winter terrains. You need to transform the terrain by "
"using terraform. This add-on should be used together with sumatran_tribe.wad."
msgstr ""
"Modifica el món per a la tribu de Sumatra. Els canvis també afecten Amazons. "
"Els arbres tropicals no creixen en terrenys hivernals. Heu de transformar el "
"terreny utilitzant terraform. Aquest complement s'ha d'utilitzar juntament "
"amb sumatran_tribe.wad."

